org.codefx.libfx.listener.handle

Interface ListenerDetachHandle

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ControlPropertyListenerHandle, ListenerHandle, NestedListenerHandle, WebViewHyperlinkListenerHandle
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    NestedChangeListenerHandle, NestedInvalidationListenerHandle

    public interface ListenerDetachHandle
    A listener handle can be used to detach a listener from some observable instance.
    See Also:
    ListenerHandle

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void detach()
      Removes the listener from the observable.

    • Method Detail

      • detach

        void detach()
        Removes the listener from the observable. Calling this method when the listener is not added is a no-op.
